I can't fully explain what is going on in the TL program, but there are some changes going on, and I personally think they are for the better.<br>
<br>
We are getting an opportunity to work much more closely with Mythic than we did in the past.<br>
<br>
I was privvy to the whole thread on the TL boards that caused Schirf to leave, and I would take what he posted on VN with a grain of salt.<br>
<br>
